messages.content: How do I make my gemini API key paid tier

To upgrade your Gemini API key to the paid tier, you need to enable billing on the associated Google Cloud project. Here's how:

1.  Go to the Google AI Studio API keys page.
2.  Select the Google Cloud project for the API key you want to upgrade.
3.  Click on "Set up Billing" or "Upgrade". This will guide you through linking a billing account in the Google Cloud console.

The paid tier provides higher rate limits and ensures your data isn't used to improve Google's products.
